resources.string: saferoad Information Technology is a Saudi based company that provides telematics solutions to the local & international market since 2009, which is owned partially by Aramco Entrepreneurship Center (Waed).

The primary goal of saferoad is to reduce accident number and to help the drivers in Saudi Arabia to enhance their driving behavior. The effective contribution of saferoad technologies in regional economy let the company get many Regional and International awards.
